## Technology Stack

### Backend
| Component | Technology | Purpose |
|-----------|------------|---------|
| **Framework** | FastAPI | High-performance async API |
| **AI Model** | Google Gemini 2.5 Flash | Conversational AI, content generation |
| **Vector DB** | FAISS | Similarity search for RAG |
| **Embeddings** | Sentence Transformers (all-MiniLM-L6-v2) | Text embedding for RAG |
| **Database** | MongoDB | User data, messages, summaries |
| **Blockchain** | Algorand (Testnet) | Consent management |
| **Voice STT** | Gemini 2.5 Flash (multimodal) | Speech-to-text |
| **Voice TTS** | ElevenLabs / gTTS | Text-to-speech |

### Frontend
| Component | Technology |
|-----------|------------|
| **HTML/CSS** | Vanilla HTML5, CSS3 |
| **JavaScript** | Vanilla ES6+ |
| **Storage** | localStorage (user session) |

