## API Endpoints

### Core Endpoints

| Endpoint | Method | Description |
|----------|--------|-------------|
| `/` | GET | Serve frontend |
| `/health` | GET | Health check |
| `/chat` | POST | Main chat interaction |
| `/voice-chat` | POST | Voice-based chat |
| `/onboarding` | POST | User registration |
| `/daily-checkin` | POST | Log daily health status |
| `/pattern-insight` | POST | Analyze health patterns |
| `/learn` | POST | Generate educational content |
| `/alert` | POST | Proactive stress alerts |
| `/summarize-session` | POST | Summarize conversation |

### Request/Response Schemas

```python
# Chat Request
{
    "user_id": "string",
    "message": "string",
    "use_rag": bool (optional)
}

# Onboarding Request
{
    "user_id": "string",
    "cycle_length": int,
    "last_period_date": "YYYY-MM-DD",
    "health_goals": ["string"],
    "concerns": ["string"] (optional)
}

# Daily Check-in Request
{
    "user_id": "string",
    "mood": "happy|confident|neutral|anxious|sad|irritable",
    "pain_level": 0-10,
    "symptoms": ["string"] (optional)
}

# Learn Request
{
    "user_id": "string",
    "topic": "string"
}
```

