## Security & Privacy

### Data Protection

| Feature | Implementation |
|---------|----------------|
| **Consent Management** | Algorand blockchain records consent hash |
| **Conditional Storage** | Messages only saved if consent verified |
| **No Diagnosis** | AI explicitly avoids medical diagnoses |
| **Professional Referral** | Serious symptoms prompt doctor consultation |

### Blockchain Consent Flow

```
┌──────────┐    ┌──────────────┐    ┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
│  User    │───▶│  record_     │───▶│  1. Hash user_id (SHA-256)          │
│  Consents│    │  consent()   │    │  2. Create Algorand transaction     │
└──────────┘    └──────────────┘    │  3. Sign with wallet mnemonic       │
                                    │  4. Submit to Algorand Testnet      │
                                    │  5. Return transaction ID           │
                                    └─────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Privacy Features
- **Graceful Degradation**: Works without Algorand wallet (dev mode)
- **In-Memory Option**: Functions without MongoDB connection
- **No External Data Sharing**: All processing happens server-side
- **Consent Check**: Every message save checks consent status

