## Setup & Installation

### Prerequisites
- Python 3.10+
- MongoDB (optional, has in-memory fallback)
- Google Gemini API Key
- ElevenLabs API Key (optional)
- Algorand Wallet (optional)

### Installation Steps

```bash
# 1. Clone the repository
git clone <repository-url>
cd shakti-app

# 2. Create virtual environment
python -m venv .venv
.venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1  # Windows PowerShell
# or
source .venv/bin/activate    # Linux/Mac

# 3. Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# 4. Configure environment
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with your API keys

# 5. Run the application
uvicorn main:app --reload --port 8000
```

### Quick Start (PowerShell)
```powershell
.\run.ps1
```

---

## Configuration

### Environment Variables (`.env`)

```env
# Required
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_google_gemini_api_key

# Optional - MongoDB (uses in-memory if not set)
MONGODB_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017/shaktidb

# Optional - Voice (falls back to gTTS if not set)
ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=your_elevenlabs_api_key
ELEVENLABS_VOICE_ID=21m00Tcm4TlvDq8ikWAM

# Optional - Blockchain (bypasses consent check if not set)
ALGORAND_MNEMONIC=your_25_word_mnemonic

# Optional - Frontend
FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:3000
```

